[[File:OublietteShadowport-Polyhedron165.png|thumb|right|250px|Oubliette]]
'''Oubliette''' was a [[Shadowport/Legends|shadowport]] hidden in the northern rim of [[Old Soren]] on the planet [[Ord Vaxal]]. It was owned and maintained by the [[Besadii/Legends|Besadii]] [[Kajidic/Legends|kajidic]] of [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]] who were represented on the planet by [[Sassallo]] the Hutt.

Most of the shadowport remained underground with the few above ground areas designed to blend in with the ruins of Old Soren. Oubliette was used as a staging ground for operations in and around [[Tof Soren]] with the purpose of capturing slaves. Oubliette was also sometimes used as a hiding place for 'hot' items and individuals.

